    <p class="section-number">Scope</p>
    <h2>What we do, and what we don't.</h2>

    <p><strong>We service:</strong> Henny Penny PFE-500, PFE-561, and predecessor PFE pressure fryer lines. BKI LPF series. Other commercial pressure fryer brands as standard coverage. Pressure-rated lid gaskets (OEM only), pressure relief valve testing and replacement, door interlock safety systems, steam venting solenoids, heating systems, integrated filtration. Annual safety inspections with documentation.</p>

    <p><strong>We don't do:</strong> aftermarket gasket substitution on pressure-rated lid gaskets (OEM only on safety-critical pressure components); pressure vessel structural repair if the chamber itself shows damage (manufacturer warranty work, not field repair); home-use or stovetop pressure cookers (different equipment category, different scope); pressure-cooker-style equipment for non-fryer applications.</p>
