      <li><strong>Henny Penny network access.</strong> Henny Penny is independent (not Welbilt) and has a robust service network. We work with their distribution for OEM parts.</li>
      <li><strong>Common Henny Penny parts on the van.</strong> PFE-500 and PFE-561 lid gaskets, pressure relief valves, door interlock components, heating elements.</li>
      <li><strong>Honest scope on aftermarket parts.</strong> We won't quote aftermarket lid gaskets to save you $200 on a pressure-rated component. The aftermarket appliance parts industry has tried; on a pressure vessel that's a safety problem, not a cost-saving opportunity.</li>
      <li><strong>$120 commercial diagnostic anytime.</strong> No emergency surcharge.</li>
